descrip: My kid used her crayons to draw her sister. She cooked :O.
A simple pond of water lilies.

Oil paint was used to emphasize the contrast between the light and the dark. Although the night enshrouds the world in darkness the light contrasts against the dark to highlight the blooming urban life. As one the nightlife of Paris comes alive.
My inspiration was that I was playing a game in which I couldn't just leave but my mom needed help buying groceries so I had to leave the game :<.
